  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Taipan is a Word of Blake quad design that came out of the Jihad-era Martinson Armaments plant on Terra, built in limited numbers before the Republic of the Sphere shut down production and the design effectively went extinct before 3090. Quadrupedal light mechs are already a niche category, and the MASC system pushing this one past 150 kph makes it genuinely difficult to engage before it has already fired and repositioned. Most of what survived ended up in museums, which makes finding a working example in the field a notable event.",
